CashAllocationCodeDetail is a Form
    is primary
    title is "CashAllocationCodeDetail"
    Layout
        paragraph
            CashAllocationCode
                display as text
            CashAllocationCode.Description
                no label
                display as text
        blank line
        single column
            AllocationAccount
                compact format
        visible when (CashAllocationCode.AllocationType.Amount)
            single column
                AllocationAmount
        visible when (CashAllocationCode.AllocationType.Percent)
            single column
                AllocationPercent
        single column
            Comment
                use text area of 3 lines
